Input:

Code
num1 = 3, num2 = -2
Try k=1 → rem = 3 - (-2) = 5 → popcount(5)=2 >1 → fail.

Try k=2 → rem = 3 - 2*(-2) = 7 → popcount(7)=3 >2 → fail.

Try k=3 → rem = 3 - 3*(-2) = 9 → popcount(9)=2 ≤3 and rem≥3 → success.
Answer = 3 ✅

